# Day 2 – ALTER, UPDATE & DELETE

## Topics Covered

- ALTER TABLE
- UPDATE
- DELETE

## ALTER TABLE

Used to change the table structure.

```sql
ALTER TABLE Student
ADD email VARCHAR(50);
```

## UPDATE

Used to modify existing records.

```sql
UPDATE Student
SET age = 21
WHERE id = 1;
```

> **Note:** Without the `WHERE` clause, every row will be updated.

## DELETE

Used to remove records.

```sql
DELETE FROM Student
WHERE id = 2;
```

### Practiced

- Add a new column.
- Rename a column.
- Update multiple records.
- Delete a single record.

